resources NI(12)
notes
We just started neutral temperature  observations between 80-110 km with a Sodium LIDAR installed at 
Ramjordmoen. This experiment aims at examining variations of the temperature between 80 and 110 km 
due to aurora effect (from above) and atmospheric wave effect (from below). 


